data.description: SELLER MOTIVATED! Step into this elegant 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath home with a study, in the established Cypress Creek Lakes community. The entire house boasts scratch and water-resistant laminate wood flooring, extending from the primary and secondary bedrooms on the second floor to every corner of this beautiful residence. Upon entry, you're welcomed by an office/study with double doors and a formal dining room, offering versatility and sophistication. The open concept in the family room and kitchen area ensures a seamless flow for daily living. A new roof, installed in June 2023, guarantees protection and peace of mind. The primary bedroom is on the first floor, and wood-stained stairs lead to the second floor, where you'll find the same resilient laminate in the game room and hallway. Upstairs, enjoy a spacious game room or media area and three additional bedrooms with a shared bathroom. Schedule your appointment today to experience all this home offers.
